Subject: [RFC/POC PATCH] block: scaffold KVIO scheduler stats

Local RFC/POC patch scaffold.

This patch reserves space for minimal KVIO observability counters:

- kvio_decode_dispatches
- kvio_prefetch_dispatches
- kvio_prefill_dispatches
- kvio_normal_dispatches
- kvio_starvation_escapes

The exact debugfs or sysfs integration is intentionally left as a TODO
because that plumbing is kernel-version-specific and secondary to the
first decode-priority experiment.

